## 4. REST API Endpoint Catalog

### Base URL
```
https://api.investtracker.io/api/v1
```

### 4.1 — Authentication

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/auth/register` | Register a new tenant + admin user | Public |
| `POST` | `/auth/login` | Login, receive JWT | Public |
| `POST` | `/auth/refresh` | Refresh access token using refresh token | JWT |
| `POST` | `/auth/logout` | Invalidate refresh token | JWT |

**POST `/auth/login` — Request Body:**
```json
{
  "email": "admin@acme.com",
  "password": "S3cur3Pass!"
}
```
**Response:**
```json
{
  "accessToken": "eyJhbGci...",
  "refreshToken": "dGhpcyBp...",
  "tokenType": "Bearer",
  "expiresIn": 3600,
  "user": {
    "id": 1,
    "email": "admin@acme.com",
    "role": "ADMIN",
    "tenantId": "acme-tenant-uuid"
  }
}
```

---

### 4.2 — Tenant Management (ADMIN only)

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Role |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/tenants/me` | Get current tenant details | ADMIN |
| `PUT` | `/tenants/me` | Update tenant name / plan | ADMIN |
| `GET` | `/tenants/me/stats` | Tenant-wide aggregate stats | ADMIN |

---

### 4.3 — User Management

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Role |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/users` | List all users in tenant | ADMIN |
| `POST` | `/users` | Invite / create a user | ADMIN |
| `GET` | `/users/{id}` | Get user by ID | ADMIN / self |
| `PUT` | `/users/{id}` | Update user profile | ADMIN / self |
| `DELETE` | `/users/{id}` | Deactivate user | ADMIN |
| `GET` | `/users/me` | Get current user profile | USER |
| `PUT` | `/users/me/password` | Change own password | USER |

---

### 4.4 — Investments (Core CRUD)

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Role |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/investments` | List investments (paginated, filtered) | USER |
| `POST` | `/investments` | Add a new investment | USER |
| `GET` | `/investments/{id}` | Get single investment detail | USER |
| `PUT` | `/investments/{id}` | Edit investment | USER |
| `DELETE` | `/investments/{id}` | Soft-delete investment | USER |
| `GET` | `/investments/summary` | Aggregate totals for dashboard | USER |
| `GET` | `/investments/top-performers` | Top N performing assets | USER |
| `POST` | `/investments/csv-upload` | Bulk upload via CSV | USER |
| `GET` | `/investments/export` | Export portfolio as CSV | USER |

**GET `/investments` — Query Parameters:**

| Param | Type | Example | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `page` | int | `0` | Page index (0-based) |
| `size` | int | `20` | Page size |
| `sort` | string | `currentValue,desc` | Sort field & direction |
| `type` | string | `STOCK` | Filter by investment type |
| `search` | string | `HDFC` | Name/symbol keyword search |

---

### 4.5 — Transactions

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Role |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/transactions` | List all transactions (paginated) | USER |
| `GET` | `/transactions/{id}` | Single transaction detail | USER |
| `GET` | `/investments/{id}/transactions` | Transactions per investment | USER |

---

### 4.6 — Dashboard & Analytics

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Role |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/dashboard/summary` | Total invested, current value, P&L | USER |
| `GET` | `/dashboard/allocation` | Investment type distribution (pie chart) | USER |
| `GET` | `/dashboard/growth` | Portfolio value over time (line chart) | USER |
| `GET` | `/dashboard/top-performers` | Top 5 best-performing assets | USER |

**GET `/dashboard/summary` — Response:**
```json
{
  "totalInvested": 500000.00,
  "currentValue": 625000.00,
  "profitLoss": 125000.00,
  "profitLossPct": 25.0,
  "investmentCount": 12,
  "currency": "INR"
}
```

---

### 4.7 — Audit Logs

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Role |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/audit-logs` | View audit trail (paginated) | ADMIN |
| `GET` | `/audit-logs/{id}` | Single audit event | ADMIN |

