## 6. Project Module Structure

```
investment-tracker/
│
├── backend/                        ← Spring Boot application
│   └── src/main/java/com/investtracker/
│       ├── config/                 ← Security, CORS, Swagger config
│       ├── controller/             ← REST controllers
│       ├── dto/                    ← Request & Response DTOs
│       ├── entity/                 ← JPA entities
│       ├── exception/              ← Custom exceptions & global handler
│       ├── filter/                 ← JwtAuthFilter, TenantFilter
│       ├── repository/             ← Spring Data JPA repositories
│       ├── security/               ← JwtUtil, UserDetailsService
│       ├── service/                ← Business logic
│       └── tenant/                 ← TenantContext, TenantInterceptor
│
├── frontend/                       ← React + Vite application
│   └── src/
│       ├── app/                    ← Redux store
│       ├── components/             ← Reusable UI components
│       │   ├── layout/             ← Sidebar, Navbar
│       │   ├── ui/                 ← StatCard, InvestmentTable, Modals
│       │   └── charts/             ← PieChart, LineChart wrappers
│       ├── features/               ← Redux slices (auth, investments)
│       ├── hooks/                  ← Custom hooks
│       ├── pages/                  ← Dashboard, Login, Investments
│       ├── routes/                 ← ProtectedRoute, AppRouter
│       └── services/               ← Axios API service layer
│
├── docker/
│   ├── backend.Dockerfile
│   ├── frontend.Dockerfile
│   └── docker-compose.yml
│
└── docs/
    ├── phase1_architecture.md      ← This document
    └── api-spec.yaml               ← OpenAPI / Swagger spec
```

