## 7. Key Design Decisions Summary

| Decision | Choice | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| Multi-tenant model | Shared schema + `tenant_id` | Cost-efficient, scalable |
| Auth | JWT (Access + Refresh tokens) | Stateless, scalable, industry standard |
| Tenant isolation | Hibernate `@Filter` | Automatic, impossible to forget in queries |
| Soft delete | `deleted_at` timestamp | Audit compliance, accidental delete recovery |
| Password hashing | BCrypt (strength 12) | Industry standard, timing-attack resistant |
| Audit logs | Separate append-only table | Compliance, non-repudiation |
| Primary keys | `BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT` for data, UUID for tenants | Performance (clustered index) + security |
| Computed financials | Calculate in service, not stored | Prevent data drift, always fresh |

